! Extending

Two kinds of extension:

''Adding cascade edges'' ‚Äî write entry / action tiddlers in your own plugin or in user tiddler space. Tag with the right tag, set `ca-*` fields, save. No JS, no widget changes. See the ''Protocol'' and ''Examples'' tabs.

''Modifying engine behaviour'' ‚Äî fork the plugin. The widget is ~500 LOC of self-contained JS. Common extension points: a new stage kind (e.g. ''form'' for multi-field input), a new selection gesture, or a custom item renderer.
